high_descs: turn around and walk to the table at the end of the room
grab an egg off of the table
turn right and walk until you reach the microwave on the right
place the egg inside of the microwave, microwave the egg, and then take the egg back out again
turn right and walk to the end of the room, then turn to the right again and walk forwards until you reach the table again
place the egg down on the table to the bottom left of the sauce pan
anns.task_desc: place a microwaved egg down on the table

high_descs: Pick up the egg from the table.
Turn around towards the microwave on the counter.
Heat up the egg and take it back out from the microwave.
Turn around towards the white table.
Place the egg to the left of the pan on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a warm egg to the left of the pan on the table.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the white table.
Pick up the egg from the table.
Take the egg and turn around to find the microwave.
Put the egg in the microwave, turn it on and off again. Take the egg out.
Take the egg and turn around to go to the white table.
Place the egg on the white table.
anns.task_desc: Heat an egg in the microwave.
